  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to lxqt-powermanagement</title>

    <para>
      The <application>lxqt-powermanagement</application> package provides the
      power management module for <application>LXQt</application>.
    </para>

    &lfs79_checked;&gcc6_checked;

